@startuml
title UML state machine diagram

state "Create Account" as CreateAccount
CreateAccount : entry / Unregistered user
CreateAccount : do / Fill details
CreateAccount : exit / Registration successful

state "Watch Videos" as WatchVideos
WatchVideos : entry / Registered user
WatchVideos : do / Watch videos
WatchVideos : exit / Completed watching

state "Upload Videos" as UploadVideos
UploadVideos : entry / Registered user
UploadVideos : do / Upload video
UploadVideos : exit / Video uploaded successfully

state "Save to Likes List" as SaveToLikesList
SaveToLikesList : entry / Watching videos
SaveToLikesList : do / Add to likes list
SaveToLikesList : exit / Added to likes list

state "View Saved Videos" as ViewSavedVideos
ViewSavedVideos : entry / Registered user
ViewSavedVideos : do / View saved videos
ViewSavedVideos : exit / Completed viewing

state "Enter Discussion Option" as EnterDiscussionOption
EnterDiscussionOption : entry / Registered user
EnterDiscussionOption : do / Enter discussion option
EnterDiscussionOption : exit / Entered discussion

[*] --> CreateAccount

CreateAccount --> WatchVideos : [Watch after account creation]
CreateAccount --> UploadVideos : [Upload after account creation]

WatchVideos --> SaveToLikesList : [Save video to likes list]
WatchVideos --> [*] : [Exit watching videos]

SaveToLikesList --> ViewSavedVideos : [View saved videos from likes list]
SaveToLikesList --> WatchVideos : [Continue watching videos]

ViewSavedVideos --> WatchVideos : [Return to watch videos]
ViewSavedVideos --> [*] : [Exit viewing saved videos]

UploadVideos --> WatchVideos : [Return to watch videos after upload]
UploadVideos --> [*] : [Exit uploading video]

EnterDiscussionOption --> WatchVideos : [Return to watch videos after discussion]
EnterDiscussionOption --> [*] : [Exit entering discussion option]

@enduml
